  <name>DockShield</name>
  <summary>Docker Container Backup and Restore for KDE Plasma</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      DockShield is a powerful desktop application for KDE Plasma that allows you to easily
      backup and restore Docker containers with an intuitive graphical interface.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Backup Docker containers with full or filesystem-only modes</li>
      <li>Automatic scheduled backups with cron-style scheduler</li>
      <li>Multiple storage backends: Local, NFS, SSH/SFTP, AWS S3</li>
      <li>Native KDE notifications for backup and restore operations</li>
      <li>Complete backup history with detailed information</li>
      <li>Configurable compression levels</li>
      <li>Integrity verification with SHA256 checksums</li>
      <li>Dark and light theme support</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      DockShield integrates seamlessly with KDE Plasma, providing a native look and feel
      while offering powerful backup and restore capabilities for your Docker containers.
    </p>
  </description>

